# .stow-local-ignore
#
# Intentionally empty. ags/@girs and ags/node_modules used to be listed here so
# stow skipped them, but they are now stowed like everything else: their symlinks
# are relative, which GNU Stow accepts (it aborts only on ABSOLUTE symlinks).
#
# Keep this file present even though it's empty — its mere existence overrides
# stow's built-in default ignore list (which would otherwise skip top-level
# README/LICENSE/COPYING and VCS dirs), preserving the prior stow behavior.
